        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " tables based on a specified email pattern and application name. It supports pagination, allowing results to be returned in pages of a specified size. The procedure first determines the application ID from the application name, then retrieves user details whose email matches the specified pattern, and finally returns the results within the specified page range."
